(1, 'gallery/21-02-2024-23-52-301708539750.jpg', 'MD. Sadam Rain', 'Full-Stack Developer', 7869948102, 'mdsadam2056@gmail.com', 'I am a dedicated and versatile Full-Stack Developer with over 3 years of experience in backend, frontend, and mobile app development. My expertise spans React, Next.js, Node.js, Laravel, and React Native, allowing me to build robust, scalable, and high-performance solutions.\r\n\r\nI am currently available for freelance work and open to full-time opportunities, where I can leverage my skills to develop innovative, user-centric applications. Passionate about delivering high-quality software, I strive to create efficient, secure, and seamless digital experiences.\r\n\r\n🚀 Let’s collaborate and turn your ideas into reality!', 1, '2024-02-06 19:26:12', '2025-03-04 08:05:16');

