(1, 'static', 'Single Page Web Application', 'Simple, Sleek, and Ready to Shine Online!', 7999, '[\"Custom design tailored to your brand.\",\"Simple and intuitive navigation.\",\"Contact form for easy communication.\",\"Social media integration.\",\"Cross-browser compatibility.\",\"Secure HTTPS.\"]', '[\"Mobile-responsive layout.\",\"Up to 5 pages (e.g., Home, About, Contact).\",\"Basic SEO optimization.\",\"Fast loading speed.\",\"Basic image optimization.\",\"Easy content updates.\"]', 'Looking for a professional, affordable website that’s simple yet effective? I specialize in creating Basic Static Websites that deliver clean, responsive designs using HTML and CSS. With features like mobile compatibility, a contact form, SEO optimization, and social media integration, I’ll help you establish a strong online presence that works seamlessly on all devices. Let’s bring your vision to life with a website that’s fast, easy to navigate, and designed to impress! Contact me today to get started.', NULL, 1, '2024-02-07 17:45:59', '2025-01-04 12:28:33'),
(3, 'standard', 'Professional Dynamic Website Development', 'Affordable, Responsive, and Ready to Impress!', 14999, '[\"Custom, responsive design tailored to your brand.\",\"Content Management System (CMS) for easy updates.\",\"E-commerce functionality (product listings, shopping cart).\",\"SEO optimization for better search engine visibility.\",\"Cross-browser and mobile compatibility.\"]', '[\"User authentication and secure login systems.\",\"Dynamic pages with personalized content.\",\"Fast loading times for improved user experience.\",\"Integration with third-party APIs and services.\",\"Scalable architecture for future growth.\"]', 'Looking for a powerful, feature-rich website? I specialize in developing Dynamic Websites that offer personalized content, interactive features, and robust functionality. With advanced technologies like PHP, Laravel, React, and Node.js, I’ll build a site that adapts to your business needs, whether it’s an e-commerce platform, content management system, or custom web application. Let’s create a website that not only looks great but also delivers seamless user experiences and business growth. Contact me today to get started!', 'recommended', 1, '2024-02-16 16:47:03', '2025-01-04 12:29:02'),
(4, 'premium', 'Premium Dynamic Website Development', 'Elevate Your Brand with Cutting-Edge, Custom Web Solutions!', 24999, '[\"Fully custom design tailored to your brand identity.\",\"Secure user authentication and membership systems.\",\"Content Management System (CMS) for easy content updates.\",\"Integration with third-party APIs and services.\",\"Custom database solutions for seamless data handling.\",\"Ongoing support and maintenance options.\"]', '[\"Advanced interactive features and user engagement tools.\",\"Scalable e-commerce solutions with product catalogs, cart, and checkout.\",\"High-level SEO optimization for improved search engine ranking.\",\"Fast, responsive design optimized for all devices and browsers.\",\"Real-time analytics and reporting tools.\"]', 'Looking for a Premium Dynamic Website that stands out? I specialize in creating high-end, fully customized websites with advanced features and top-notch functionality. Using cutting-edge technologies like React, Laravel, and Node.js, I’ll build a website that offers seamless user experiences, secure user interactions, and interactive elements tailored to your business needs. Whether you need e-commerce solutions, complex databases, or a sophisticated content management system, I’ll deliver a scalable, high-performance website that drives results. Let\'s build a premium digital presence that elevates your brand and maximizes your online potential!', NULL, 1, '2024-02-16 17:13:54', '2025-01-04 12:29:39');

